title: Sunday's TV pick: Homeland returns for series five
text:
Submit 
Â© Channel 4 Season five of Homeland kicks off and we pick things up two years after the embassy attack in Islamabad. Carrie is no longer with the CIA as she struggles to reconcile her guilt and disillusionment after years of working on the front lines in the War on Terror. Her exile is self-imposed as she builds a new life working in Berlin as head of security for a German philanthropist. But how long can she keep her past buried?When her boss forces her back towards the dangerous world she left behind, will her old friends and colleagues be on hand to help Carrie once more? Homeland, Channel 4, 9pm
